lementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-e789e94 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"e789e94\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-a8339f3\" data-id=\"a8339f3\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a3e28e3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a3e28e3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Termites are real nightmares to property owners around (AREA) because of the huge damage they make. These pests primarily feed on wood, which is why people around (AREA) hire reputable removal companies to perform intensive termite control to every year, especially during the spring season. Not completing a termite removal can cost you a whole fortune! Termites will not only damage the entire structure of your house but they will also feed on insulation, books, paper, filtration systems and other parts of your property! Restoring all the damaged areas will be much more difficult than simply ordering a termite removal service at ACME.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-2b1c7ac\" data-id=\"2b1c7ac\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2d678e3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"2d678e3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t